{"title":"NAIF","description":"\u003cp\u003eLess is more, but only with the right active ingredients. Exactly what fathers Jochem and Sjoerd thought in 2013 when they had children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo Naïf was born: a reliable, no-nonsense skin care brand for babies and children. Pure quality, with only ingredients that a baby really needs. Nothing more, nothing less.\u003cbr\u003eAs it turned out, many women also liked to use Naïf's children's products.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo a women's line was created. A complete skincare line with natural care products, without chemical junk, that every woman needs in her daily beauty routine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNaïf products do not contain mineral oils, micro-plastics, chemical preservation or hard chemicals.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 is developed for the sensitive skin of a baby and kids with a reef-friendly formula. \u003cspan\u003eThe zinc-oxide based mineral filter protects the skin immediately against UVA and UVB with minimum risk of skin irritation. The convenient spray makes for a quick and easy application. Immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the spray before use. Apply a generous amount to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eDecyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Alcohol, Triheptanoin, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Aqua\/Water, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Pongamol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Denatonium Benzoate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBottle made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445499142471,"sku":"","price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml-887359.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 is developed for the sensitive skin with a reef-friendly formula and is\u003cspan\u003e suitable for the whole family. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately against UVA and UVB with minimum risk of skin irritation. The convenient spray makes for a quick and easy application.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHigh protection of sensitive skin with mineral UV filter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWater-resistant: Enjoy the water safely\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReef-friendly: no oxybenzone, octinoxate, and octocrylene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn convenient spray, so easy and quick to apply to the skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the spray before use. Apply a generous amount to the body and face before you go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Decyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Alcohol, Triheptanoin, Parfum\/Fragrance, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Aqua\/Water, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Pongamol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Denatonium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBottle made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445503205703,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-100ml-4393539.jpg?v=1753967197"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen SPF50 for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 is developed for the sensitive skin of a baby and kids with a reef-friendly formula. \u003cspan\u003eThe zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe zinc oxide based UV filter adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects the sunbeams. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation. The added natural oils make application easy and hydrates the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the sunscreen before use. Apply a generous amount evenly to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eDecyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Triheptanoin, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Dextrin Palmitate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Tocopherol, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Pongamol, Palmitic Acid.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445547737415,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml-103208.png?v=1739897347"},{"product_id":"naif-plastic-free-wipes-54pcs","title":"NAIF Plastic Free Wipes 54pcs","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif baby wipes clean and protect the baby's bum, body and face. The lotion is made from 99% water and does not contain perfume and alcohol. Suitable for sensitive and dry skin. Naif wipes are plastic free and are prepared from wood-based fibers sourced from sustainably managed forests.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile changing, open the package with one hand, holding your baby with the other. Wipe the area well and don't forget the folds. When finished, close the package tightly to prevent dehydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua\/Water, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Levulinic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445910675783,"sku":null,"price":3.95,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-plastic-free-wipes-54pcs-717208.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF 2-in-1 Shampoo \u0026 Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e2-in-1 kids Shampoo \u0026amp; Conditioner for all hairtypes (long, short, thick or curly). The shampoo cleanses your hair while the anti-tangle formula ensures that the hair is soft and easy to comb through. Softens and detangles hair and hydrates with sunflower- and linseed oil. For all kids. Without SLES or microplastics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMild, fruity scent developed for and by children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eTake a coin-sized amount of Naif 2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner and massage into wet hair. Leave it in for a bit, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Inulin, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445993644359,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-851648.png?v=1739897337"},{"product_id":"naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Nourishing Shampoo for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA nourishing shampoo developed specifically to tame those wild kids' hairs. The shampoo cleanses and softens the hair to make it easier to comb through. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaif's kids shampoo contains a special anti-tangle formula and is packed with a selection of natural ingredients, like cottonseed extract and hydrolyzed wheat protein. Cares for both hair and scalp, without microplastics, silicones and SLES. So, it’s mild for the eyes too.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a coin-sized amount of shampoo and massage into wet hair, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446040371527,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml-208574.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Softening Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCurly hair, coarse hair, thick hair - Naïf's Kids Conditioner nourishes and softens the hair of our little ones and makes it easy to comb through. Thanks to the addition of cottonseed oil, the hair is not only cared for, but also frizz-free. Suitable for all hair types.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eRemoves tangles and moisturizes the hair with sunflower and linseed oil. No SLES and microplastics. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMild and fruity fragrance - developed by and for kids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eUse the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Distearoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate, Stearamidopropyl Dimethylamine, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Behentrimonium Chloride, Dipropylene Glycol, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446052004167,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-924525.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","title":"NAIF Easy Styling Hair Lotion for Baby \u0026 Kids 150ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA hair lotion to tame and take care of wild kids hair. Naïf's Easy Styling Hair Lotion makes combing easier and reduces tangles and frizz for all hair types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHair lotion with natural ingredients that doesn't make the hair greasy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoftens knots and tangles in the hair and reduces frizz in curls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCan also be used with cradle cap\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eFor use on babies and children, for all hairtypes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES or silicones\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSpray on towel-dried hair from 30 cm away. Massage gently, comb through the hair and style. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Methylpropanediol, Caprylyl\/Capryl Glucoside, Glycerin, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Inulin, Betaine, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-6 Oleate, Sodium Surfactin, Parfum\/Fragrance (allergen-free), Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446066323783,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml-404694.png?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml","title":"NAIF Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026 Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWorry-free fun in the bath with lots of bubbles made with natural ingredients. Naif Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026amp; Kids nurtures, cleanses mildly, hydrates and promises plenty of fun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBath foam with natural derivatives from coconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and hydrates the skin while bathing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eFill the bath and add a dash of bath foam to the bath water. Mix until you see the first bubbles appear.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Parfum, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Herbaceum Seed Extract, Glyceryl Oleat, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Glycol Distearate, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube\/bottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446184714567,"sku":"","price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-200ml-869986.png?v=1739897344"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml","title":"NAIF Cleansing Wash Gel 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaïf cleansing wash gel for baby \u0026amp; kids cleanses the skin mildly and prevents dry skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWashing gel for bath and shower\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and cares for the sensitive baby skin with natural oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWithout microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount to the baby's skin. Rinse off and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside (\u003ci\u003ecloudy liquid derived from coconut\u003c\/i\u003e), Sodium Coco-Sulfate (\u003ci\u003emade from the fatty acids of coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Cocamidopropyl Betaine (\u003ci\u003enaturally-derived surfactant that is sourced from coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance (allergen-free), Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446208602439,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-254915.png?v=1739897263"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-copy","title":"NAIF Zinc Diaper Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eA zinc cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. Helps with and prevents diaper rash. No perfume added and suitable for damaged skin. \u003c\/span\u003eZinc dehydrates the skin, which is exactly what is needed to prevent or take care of diaper rash. Diapers prevent the air from circulating, resulting in wet and soft skin. This combined with pee and poo makes the skin extra sensitive to irritation and rashes.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eBaby diaper cream with natural ingredients like zinc oxide, camomile and vitamin E\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSoothes and repairs skin irritations and diaper rash\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eUse also for diaper rash prevention, after every diaper change\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eOpen the tube with one hand. Apply a small amount to the dry and clean baby bum. Spread lightly. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Sorbitan Olivate, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Glycerin, Magnesium Sulfate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446219022663,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-zinc-diaper-cream-75ml-526868.png?v=1739897265"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Baby Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNurturing Cream is a hydrating cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The cream nourishes dry and sensitive skin. With the help of sweet almond oil, avocado oil and macadamia oil the nurturing cream takes care of dry and sensitive skin and gives it some extra love. Suitable for body and face.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eMade with the best natural ingredients like sweet almond oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eFor use on face and body\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eNo microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eDermatologically tested\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of nurturing cream, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Glycerin, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446277808455,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml-913283.png?v=1739897268"},{"product_id":"naif-baby-balm-75ml-1","title":"NAIF Baby Balm 75ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eA multi-purpose balm to give dry skin some extra love. This balm with natural ingredients supports and protects the skin barrier. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNaïf Baby Balm 0% Perfume is a multi-purpose balm that forms a protective layer on dry (baby) skin which helps keep the moisture in. The balm softens skin and keeps it supple without completely closing off. Use it for dry cheeks or hands, chapped lips, sore nipples post-breastfeeding. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBalm with natural ingredients for extra dry baby skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoothes and restores the very youngest skin and supports the skin barrier\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNo animal fats, microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% perfume\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eApply a small amount of salve, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eButyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Tribehenin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract, Carica Papaya (Papaya) Fruit Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid (Sunflower Seed) Oil, Tocopherol, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446295404871,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-baby-balm-75ml-548036.png?v=1741554716"},{"product_id":"naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml-1","title":"NAIF Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026 Kids 500ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWorry-free fun in the bath with lots of bubbles made with natural ingredients. Naif Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026amp; Kids nurtures, cleanses mildly, hydrates and promises plenty of fun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBath foam with natural derivatives from coconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and hydrates the skin while bathing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Fill the bath and add a dash of bath foam to the bath water. Mix until you see the first bubbles appear.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Parfum, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Herbaceum Seed Extract, Glyceryl Oleat, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Glycol Distearate, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube\/bottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49525867938119,"sku":null,"price":15.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml-125036.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe multitasking Naïf Nurturing Day Cream hydrates and protects face, neck and décolleté during the day from the harmful effects of UV radiation. Al this thanks to the added tomato extract. To support the natural skin process, the day cream contains natural oils, such as avocado and almond oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe day cream is quickly absorbed and you don't need much of it. That's why you'll be able to use the bioplastic tube's content even longer. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the Nurturing Day Cream evenly (you don't need much) to a cleansed face, neck and décolleté.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe natural SPF6 from tomato extract provides for protection against harmful UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed Seed) Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Solanum Lycopersicum (Tomato Fruit\/Leaf\/Stem) Extract, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary Leaf) Extract, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915540205895,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-773702.png?v=1739897170"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNaïf Nurturing Night Cream contributes to a good night's sleep. The regenerating night cream soothes the skin and supports the natural skin process. Includes almond oil, shea butter and macadamia extract for ultimate hydration and moisture retention. No more dry spots!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream absorbs quickly, doesn't stick and doesn't make the skin feel tight. So you don't have to worry when resting your head on your pillow. The night cream is made without mineral oils, microplastics and silicones.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Naïf regenerating night cream is for every skin type. So also for the most sensitive skin. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eA night cream is best applied if you apply a good, thick amount. Do this on clean, cleansed skin. And don't forget to apply it to the neck and décolleté. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/ Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Methylpropanediol, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Sucrose Stearate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus, (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915767255367,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml-623217.png?v=1739897168"},{"product_id":"naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml","title":"NAIF Circular Face Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Circular Face Scrub cleanses your skin and removes dead skin cells, stimulating cell renewal. Result: radiant skin. The face scrub also contains natural oils, such as macadamia, avocado and sweet almond oil. These ingredients condition your skin and keep your skin soft and supple, without making your face feel tight, after exfoliating. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are 100% vegan, made with a gentle fragrance and are dermatologically tested, free from the 26 most common allergens. Mild for the skin, due to the fine grain, which also allows you to use the scrub several times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eScrub your face once or twice a week for beautiful, healthy skin. Slightly moisten your face and apply the pea-sized scrub to the inside of your hand. Using your fingers, massage the scrub onto your face for at least 30 seconds using circular motions. Rinse with lukewarm water. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Calcium Carbonate, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Methylpropanediol, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Parfum, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Phenylpropanol, Bisabolol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915785441607,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml-570470.png?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-face-wash-100ml","title":"NAIF Cleansing Face Wash 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gel transforms into a milky formula on contact with water. The advantage of this gel-to-milk formula is that it cleanses the skin without drying it out. Therefore, this face cleanser is suitable for all skin types, even for very oily or sensitive skin and the thinner skin around the eyes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBecause the facial cleanser contains natural oils, the skin's PH level remains undisturbed and the skin feels moisturized and supple afterward.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested, and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMoisten the face with lukewarm water. Apply a fingertip-sized amount of gel to a (washable) cotton pad or in the palm of your hand and massage the gel all over your face. The gel will now have a milky texture and slowly foams. After cleansing, rinse with lukewarm water, pat skin dry and apply a nourishing day or night cream. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHelianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Glycerin, Aqua\/Water, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Sucrose Palmitate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Caprylyl Glycol, Tocopherol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915798712647,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cleansing-face-wash-100ml-376187.png?v=1739897186"},{"product_id":"naif-milky-bath-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Milky Bath Oil for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA bath oil that takes care of your baby’s skin from the first bath onwards and softens the bath water. Gently cleanses and moisturizes your (newborn) baby's skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Bath Oil does not contain microplastics, mineral oils and parabens. Includes linseed oil: hydrating and suitable for sensitive skin and 100% natural.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eFill the baby bath and add about 10 ml (a few drops) of bath oil to the bath water. Mix for a moment so that the oil is evenly distributed. For some extra care, apply a baby oil after washing your baby.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate, Parfum\/fragrance, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915806544199,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-milky-bath-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml-696777.png?v=1739897192"},{"product_id":"naif-soothing-baby-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Soothing Baby Oil for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA nice oil that nourishes the skin, absorbs quickly and is not sticky. Use it to create a warm bonding moment with your baby during a massage. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishes and hydrates sensitive baby skin after bath time.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy adding sunflower seed oil and cottonseed oil the Naïf Baby Oil helps to lock in moisture post-bath time, so the skin doesn’t get dry and the natural protective layer of your baby’s skin stays intact. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse a few drops on the skin or in the hand and gently massage the oil in circular motions. Absorbs quickly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Parfum\/fragrance, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Gossypium (Cotton Seed) Oil, Bisabolol\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915812016455,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-soothing-baby-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml-192649.png?v=1739897180"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-0-perfume-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen 0% Perfume for Baby \u0026 Kids SPF50 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral Sunscreen SPF50 is sunscreen for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe sunscreen contains zinc-oxide: a natural ingredient that adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects sunbeams. The sunscreen also does not contain added perfume, which makes it suitable for even the most sensitive skin. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation. The added natural oils make application easy and hydrates the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Protects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15327,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}'\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eWater-resistant formula\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eDermatologically tested, 0% perfume for extra sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the sunscreen before use. Apply a generous amount evenly to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Decyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Caprylic\/Capric\/Myristic\/Stearic Triglyceride, Dextrin Palmitate, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Triheptanoin, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Palmitic Acid, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Oryzanol, Bisabolol, Pongamol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084419760455,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-100ml-633941.png?v=1741554339"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-stick-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-36g","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen Stick 0% Perfume for Baby \u0026 Kids SPF50 36g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral Sunscreen Stick SPF50 is a sunscreen for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation. Easy to take and to apply, even by kids who want to do everything themselves. Without added perfume and suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe sunscreen contains zinc-oxide: a natural ingredient that adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects sunbeams. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWater-resistant formula\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDermatologically tested, 0% perfume for extra sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a generous amount to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Make sure to spread it well. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for maximum protection\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCaprylic\/Capric\/Myristic\/Stearic Triglyceride, Zinc Oxide, Helianthus Annuus Seed Cera, Hydrogenated Rapeseed Oil, Tocopherol, Pongamol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Ascorbyl Palmitate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084446499143,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-stick-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-36g-964551.png?v=1741554338"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf30-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen SPF30 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral Sunscreen SPF30 is sunscreen suitable for the whole family. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe zinc oxide based UV filter adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects the sunbeams. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation. The added natural oils make application easy.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}'\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}'\u003eWater-resistant formula\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"0\",\"3\":1},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":1},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Dermatologically tested\"}' data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eDermatologically tested\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eShake before use! Apply a generous amount of sunscreen evenly to the body and face before you go out in the sun. This sunscreen offers immediate protection! Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimal protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBe aware that zinc oxide, the sun and water can have a dehydrating effect on the skin. Make sure to rehydrate the skin with an after sun or a nourishing cream after a day in the sun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Decyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Caprylic\/Capric\/Myristic\/Stearic Triglyceride, Dextrin Palmitate, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Triheptanoin, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Parfum\/Fragrance, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Palmitic Acid, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Oryzanol, Bisabolol, Pongamo\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084465668423,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf30-100ml-826299.png?v=1740228553"},{"product_id":"naif-lotion-baby-wipes-54pcs","title":"NAIF Lotion Baby Wipes 54pcs","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf plastic-free lotion wipes are everything you would expect from a baby wipe: strong, well moisturized, with ingredients that take good care of the sensitive baby skin. Does not include polyester fibers and microplastics. Also suitable as a nose cleaner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy using extra (vegetable) glycerin, aloe vera and bamboo for extra hydration and prematurely soothing red baby bottoms. The lotion has been dermatologically tested and does not contain alcohol, perfume or other ingredients that can cause red baby's buttocks.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile changing, open the package with one hand, holding your baby with the other. Wipe the area well and don't forget the folds. When finished, close the package tightly to prevent dehydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Bambusa Arundinacea Stem (Bamboo) Extract, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Levulinic Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice Powder, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084485984583,"sku":null,"price":3.95,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-lotion-baby-wipes-54pcs-938646.jpg?v=1740228550"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-copy","title":"NAIF Cooling Aftersun 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Cooling After Sun Gel soothes, moisturizes and restores the skin after a sunny day. Aloe Vera provides cooling and regeneration, glycerine for hydration. This keeps even the most sensitive skin soft and supple. Just what the skin needs after exposure to UV rays. Also nice: absorbs quickly and doesn't leave a sticky layer.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply generously after exposure to the sun. Especially on the areas that have had a lot of sun. Repeat if skin still feels dry.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTip: Keep the gel in the refrigerator, so it is extra cooling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice Powder, Allantoin, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are vegan, made with a mild fragrance and dermatologically tested, without the 26 most common allergens. They also do not contain SLES or microplastics. The tubes are made from sugar cane-based bioplastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52037698814279,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cooling-aftersun-100ml-5567632.png?v=1753967377"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/collections\/naif-483642.webp?v=1739979848","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/naif.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}